com.ibm.team.process.common.advice.runtime
Class OperationAdviceListener

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.team.process.common.advice.runtime.OperationAdviceListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
IOperationAdviceListener
public class OperationAdviceListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements IOperationAdviceListener

This listener provides default implementations for the methods defined in IOperationAdviceListener. The default implementations do nothing.

Classes that wish to listen to operation advice events can extend this class and override only the methods which they are interested in.

Since:
0.5
